<br>
Line 1: /pause 10,/auction half of long text<br>
Line 2: /auction other half of long text<br>
<br>
You can also abbreviate the commands like follows, this saves some space so you can have longer auction text:<br>
<br>
Line 1: /pau 10,/auc half of long text<br>
Line 2: /auc other half of long text<br>
<br>
If you only have two or three lines of text you can also move the pauses to another line to make more space for the auction, like follows:<br>
<br>
Line 1: /auc Half of long text<br>
Line 2: /pause 10<br>
Line 3: /auc Other half of long text <p><I>~Dart</I></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=2566.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=2566.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2566.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=2566.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.threadControl?topicID=2566.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2566.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2566.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub42.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="ayonaerofrm1">General Forum<option value="ayonaerofrm6">NAG (Nearly Anything Goes)<option value="ayonaerofrm7">The Bazaar<option value="ayonaerofrm12">Nuggets<option value="ayonaerofrm8">Raid Forum<option value="ayonaerofrm9">Polls, Tests & Beyond<option value="ayonaerofrm10">Roleplay